'''Political Reliability Observers''' oversaw ranking members of the [[Imperial Military/Legends|Imperial Military]] to ensure that they, or those they were close to, did not say or act in ways that were critical of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] and the [[New Order/Legends|New Order]].

==Behind the scenes==
The concept of Political Reliablity Observers was introduced in the ''[[Dark Empire Sourcebook]]'', which was released in [[June]] of [[1993]].

